OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,FPart of a Paddington Bear display in
OL,7,FSouthampton which was vandalised has
OL,8,Fbeen returned to the city centre.
OL,10,FThe bench that the statue of the much
OL,11,Floved character was sitting on in
OL,12,FGuildhall Square was damaged earlier
OL,13,Fthis month.
OL,15,FA nearby cafe took the statue inside
OL,16,Ffor safe-keeping, and now repairs have
OL,17,Ftaken place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
