OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777579557
OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,FOne of 23 statues, Paddington first
OL,7,Farrived in Southampton in October 2024
OL,8,Fas part of a UK-wide trail celebrating
OL,9,Fthe release of 'Paddington in Peru'.
OL,11,FExecutive Director of GO! Southampton
OL,12,FStephen Manion said: "It's great to
OL,13,Fsee Paddington Bear back in the heart
OL,14,Fof the city bringing joy to passers-by.
OL,16,F"We've seen lots of supportive
OL,17,Fcomments online from those keen to
OL,18,Fhave him back. It really shows just
OL,19,Fhow much he means to the community.
OL,26,@tD@VOU
