OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777579557
OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,F"Paddington has become one of the city
OL,7,Fcentre's gems ever since he settled to
OL,8,Ftuck into his signature sandwich
OL,9,Foutside Westquay in 2024.
OL,11,F"I'd like to thank BB Merchants and
OL,12,Fthe Garden Society for their support
OL,13,Freinstating the statue to its former
OL,14,Fglory ` he's looking happier than
OL,15,Fever!"
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@FO]
