OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777579557
OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,FNeil Fillbrook, Group CEO, BB Merchant
OL,7,FServices said: "I was saddened to hear
OL,8,Fof the vandalism to the bench, but
OL,9,Frather than comment about how dreadful
OL,10,Fit was, as a locally based global
OL,11,Femployer, I wanted to offer tangible
OL,12,Fhelp.
OL,14,F"As Paddington would say: 'If you're
OL,15,Fkind and polite, the world will be
OL,16,Fright.' I'm with the righteous bear on
OL,17,Fthis and it's such an important
OL,18,Fmessage that resonates today more so
OL,19,Fthan ever before.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
