FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777579557
OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,FThat said, unlike Paddington, I prefer
OL,7,Fmy marmalade shred-less and always
OL,8,Ftold my dear departed mum to always
OL,9,F"remove the worms!" So that's where he
OL,10,Fand I differ slightly in our world
OL,11,Foutlook!"
OL,13,FPCSO Jimi Noyce, who is leading the
OL,14,Finvestigation said: "The Paddington
OL,15,Fbench was a muchloved feature in our
OL,16,Fcommunity, and seeing it vandalised
OL,17,Fwas hugely disheartening for many
OL,18,Fpeople.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@SO]sD@IO]vD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
