PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777579557
OL,3,CPaddington Bear display returns to
OL,4,Ccity centre after being vandalised
OL,6,F"I'm really pleased to see Paddington
OL,7,Freturning to his rightful place now
OL,8,Fthe bench has been restored.
OL,10,F"Our investigation into the damage
OL,11,Fremains ongoing as we continue to
OL,12,Freview CCTV and follow all available
OL,13,Flines of enquiry to identify those
OL,14,Fresponsible."
